  Page: 218
  Verse: 1
Tags:
  - Habits
---
vp* After the mind has become accustomed to create a certain routine of
thought, it likes to go on creating. ...in exactly the same way. It always
loves its own way, and it can never believe that any other way is quite as
good as its own. ...Mind adores routine.
